(10, 'Gorizia', '06/11/1984', '', 'Tino84.jpg', 'Dimmu Borgir, Cannibal Corpse, Darkthrone, Decrepit Birth, Grave, Morbid Angel, Marduk, Origin, Opera IX, Sex Pistols,\r\nRebaelliun, Sonata Arctica, White Skull, Hour of Penance, Immortal, Malevolent Creation, Suffocation,\r\nFreddie King, Norah Jones', 'Death, Brutal, Black, musica in generale', 'Informatica, musica, hi-fi, fotografia, romanzi, cinema, sport, attualità'),
(11, 'Torino', '14/04/1985', '', 'metalraw.jpg', 'Rush; Judas Priest; Devin Townsend/Strapping Young Lad; Fear Factory; Machine Head; Diablo; Manowar; Savatage;\r\nJohn Oliva; Meat Loaf; Queen; Black Sabbath; Blind Guardian; Between the Buried and Me; Mastodon; Tesseract;\r\nPink Floyd; Voivod; Unearth; Heaven Shall Burn; Ghost; Paradise Lost; Five Finger Death Punch; Lamb of God;\r\nMercyful Fate; The Cult; Journey; Baroness; Death SS; R.J. Dio; Magnum; Rage; Disturbed; Marillion; Type O Negative;\r\nUltravox; Foo Fighters; Deftones; Coheed and Cambria; Queensrÿche; Def Leppard; Yes; Boston; Edguy/Avantasia;\r\nBlessed by a Broken Heart; Gamma Ray; Trivium; As I Lay Dying; Iced Earth; Soulfly; Anthrax', 'Classic/Heavy Metal; Progressive Rock/Metal; Thrash Metal; Metalcore; Southern Rock; AOR e, in generale,\r\ntutta la buona musica, heavy e non...', 'Musica, Sceneggiatura, Fumetti, Giocattoli, Collezionismo folle ed esagerato, Cinema, Calcio, Fantascienza e Fisica Quantistica'),
(12, 'Milano', '12/06/1982', '', 'Irastrana.jpg', 'Mayhem, Gorgoroth, Marduk, Morbid Angel, Cannibal Corpse, Deicide, Brutal Truth, Impaled Nazarene, Obituary,\r\nDeath, Carcass, Nile, Gigi D''Alessio (te l''ho fatta, eh?) ecc.', 'Death, Brutal, Grind, Swing anni 40 (a sto giro non è uno scherzo)', 'Scrittura, moto e motori, velocità in generale e grandi altezze, capoeira e i perché.'),
(13, 'Limbiate (MB)', '08/05/1992', '', 'Kriegsphilosophie.jpg', 'Morbid Angel, Incantation, Immolation, Suffocation, Death, Asphyx, Deeds Of Flesh, Antropofagus, Electrocution, \r\nGorement, Vomitory, Deicide, Marduk, Burzum, Darkthrone, Immortal, Beherit, Necrophagist, \r\nSpawn Of Possession, Demilich e tanti altri', 'Death, Black, Doom, Shoegaze, Witch House', 'Grafica, pittura e arte in generale, suonare il basso elettrico, politica'),
(14, 'Triuggio (Monza e Brianza)', '04/12/1995', '', 'Nicko.jpg', 'In ambito death, Morbid Angel, Immolation, Incantation, vecchi Entombed, Asphyx, Grave, Obituary, Bolt Thrower,\r\nprimi Suffocation e Nile, e ovviamente gli omonimi del genere, come gruppo di iniziazione. In quello thrash, direi Slayer,\r\nKreator, Exodus, Coroner, Possessed, e generalmente i dischi anni ''80. Per quello black, primi Mayhem, primi Marduk,\r\nDissection, Rotting Christ, Necrophobic.', 'Death metal, thrash metal, black metal, generalmente nelle loro accezioni più "old school"', 'Musica (ovviamente), suonare, concerti, università'),
(15, 'Treviso/Padova', '12/07/1988', '', 'GioMaster.jpg', 'Anorexia Nervosa, Novembre, Opeth, Katatonia, October Tide, Djerv, Le Grand Guignol, Vulture Industries, Axamenta,\r\nSwallow The Sun, Blind Guardian, Stormlord, Behemoth, At The Gates, Insomnium, Scar Symmetry, Wintersun, Miseration,\r\nAgrypnie, Deathspell Omega, Wolves In The Throne Room, Ne Obliviscaris, Pantheon I, Carach Angren, Deathcode Society,\r\nImperial Vengeance, Transcending Bizarre?, Soulfallen, The Breathing Process, In Lingua Mortua, Emperor, Immortal,\r\nZonaria, Dimmu Borgir, Cradle Of Filth, Children Of Bodom, Dark Tranquillity, In Flames, Universum, The Foreshadowing,\r\nAtoma, Powerwolf, Daylight Dies, Ade, Bloodbath, Fleshgod Apocalypse, Septicflesh, The Faceless, Obscura', 'Black, Death e Doom in particolare, ma anche molta musica classica.', 'Musica, Scienza, Letteratura, Filosofia, Attività Fisica, Cucina.'),
(16, 'Ferrara', '24/02/1994', '', 'Arvssynd.jpg', 'Drapsnatt, Bathory, Moonsorrow, Menhir, Enslaved, Burzum, Windir, Vreid, Darkthrone, Manegarm, Helheim, Falkenbach,\r\nImmortal, Taake, Empyrium, Silencer, Nyktalgia, Primordial, Nokturnal Mortum, Peste Noire, Orphaned Land,\r\nMoss of Moonlight, Malnatt, Movimento d''Avanguardia Ermetico, In Tormentata Quiete, Frangar, Deadly Carnage, Ianva.', 'Viking, Folk, Pagan, Black (in tutte le sue sfumature), Doom, Sludge, Shoegaze/Post-rock, Neo-folk/Darkwave', 'Musica, chitarra elettrica, sport (in televisione), collezionismo'),
(17, 'Isole Faroe', '08/12/1991', '', 'Akaah.jpg', 'Depeche Mode, Hamferð, Eivør Pálsdóttir, Sigur Rós, The Birthday Massacre, Björk, Ulver, Immortal, Darkthone,\r\nAzaghal (pre 2010), Ihsahn, Behemoth, Moonsorrow, Deicide, Decapitated, Gojira, Cannibal Corpse, Suffocation, Death,\r\nSunn O))), Pain, VCMG, Nachtmahr, Rammstein, Mr. Bungle, Petri Nygård, Notkea Rotta, Kauko Röyhkä, Xaviaro', 'Black, doom e death metal in tutte le loro sfumature, elettronica, industrial, jazz', 'Lingue e letterature, scandinavistica e finnistica, traduzioni, film, letture amene e non'),
(18, 'Padova', '23/09/1985', '', 'Kara.jpg', 'Einherjer, Finntroll, Korpiklaani, Turisas, Týr, Folkstone, Saltatio Mortis, Subway to Sally, Rotting Christ, Immortal,\r\nBurzum, At the Gates, Hypocrisy, Skeletonwitch, My Dying Bride, Black Sabbath, Iron Maiden, Motörhead, Blind Guardian,\r\nPowerwolf, Cathedral, Dropkick Murphys, Mad Sin, ASP, Kirlian Camera, Faith and the Muse, Sopor Aeternus, Faun,\r\nOmnia, Bauhaus, Virgin Prunes, Nick Cave and the Bad Seeds, Editors, Franz Ferdinand.', 'Folk, viking, black, heavy, power, folk rock, mittelalter rock.', 'Suonare il violino, studiare le lingue, letteratura, giochi da tavolo, giocoleria.'),
(19, 'Chivasso (TO)', '05/05/1991', '', 'Room101.jpg', 'Black Sabbath (Periodo Dio), Iron Maiden, Blind Guardian, Delain, Epica, Sonata Arctica, Rhapsody of Fire, Dream Theater,\r\nEdguy, Immortal, Metallica, Nightwish, Tarot, Ayreon, Avantasia, Lacuna Coil, Manowar, Orphaned Land,\r\nThe Foreshadowing, Folkstone, Ensiferum, Kamelot, Swallow the Sun, Draconian, The 3rd and the Mortal, Ulver,\r\nAfter Forever, Slayer, Type 0 Negative, Within Temptation, Sabaton and many more!', 'Heavy, Gothic, Symphonic, Doom, Folk, e Power principalmente ma non disdegno il Progressive,\r\nalcuni gruppi Black e il Death Melodico.', 'Filosofia, Letteratura, Basso elettrico, Home Recording e sport vari.'),
(20, 'Sardegna', '', '', '5_HT.jpg', 'Daylight Dies, Swallow The Sun, Slumber, October Tide, Novembre, Draconian, The Foreshadowing, Enshine, Hamferð,\r\nAt The Gates, The Haunted, Hatesphere, Dark Tranquillity, Carnal Forge, Mors Principium Est, Carcass,\r\nArch Enemy (era Johan Liiva), Aeon, Deicide, Cryptopsy, Deeds of Flesh, Disavowed, Severe Torture,\r\nCenturian, Incantation, ...', 'Doom, Death, Thrash', 'Musica, musica e musica, suonare il basso, malattie e disturbi mentali, storia, archeologia, località improbabili.'),
(21, 'Verolengo (TO)', '10/01/1992', '', 'Arianrhod.jpg', 'Epica, Ensiferum, Within Temptation, Nightwish, Eluveitie, Tristania, Mayan, Sonata Arctica, After Forever, Arkona,\r\nBlind Guardian, Apocalyptica, Swallow The Sun', 'Symphonic, Gothic, Folk, Doom, Power Metal ma anche Musica Classica e Celtica', 'Scrittura, chitarra, letteratura, antropologia, lingue straniere'),
(22, 'Genova', '27/01/1982', '', 'Er_Trucido.jpg', 'Metallica, Megadeth, Slayer, Anthrax, Exodus, Sodom, Overkill, Motorhead, Iron Maiden, Sepultura, Kreator, Testament,\r\nOpeth, Obituary, Morbid Angel, Machine Head, Death, Voivod, Carcass, Napalm Death, Grip Inc., S.O.D. , Led Zeppelin,\r\nBlack Sabbath, Litfiba, Elio e le storie tese e tanti altri metal e non!', 'Thrash Metal, Death Metal, Hard Rock, Grindcore, Heavy metal', 'Musica, videogiochi, fumetti, sport, fantacalcio'),
(23, 'Roma', '12/06/1989', '', 'Stjarna.jpg', 'Spazz, Despise You, Napalm Death, Agoraphobic Nosebleed, Devourement, Amebix, Anal Cunt, Regurgitate,\r\nRudimentary Peni, Gut, Desaster, Repulsion, Cough, Vitamin X, Skruigners, Disfear, Negazione, Grandine, Sunn O))),\r\nInquisition, Necros Christos, Sarcofago, Kraftwerk, Einsturzende Neubauten, Sisters of Mercy, Depeche Mode,\r\nDarkthrone, Alien Sex Fiend, Clan of Xymox... e mi fermo qui altrimenti vado ad oltranza!', 'Grind, Brutal, Poweviolence, Crust, Hardcore Punk, Anarcho-punk/oi, D-beat, Noise, Power Electronics,Death Old School,\r\nThrash Old School, Black Metal, Black/Death, Black/Thrash, Doom, Drone, Sludge, Dark Wave, Synth Pop, Elettronica,\r\nAmbient, Dark Ambient', 'Arte, Musica, Libri, il Vino di mio nonno, la Birra e il Kebab.'),
(24, 'Roma', '22/12/1989', '', 'Blackout.jpg', 'Asphyx, Incantation, Bolt Thrower, Autopsy, Order from Chaos, Sadistik Exekution, Infester, Angelcorpse, Pentagram,\r\nBlasphemy, Archgoat, Saint Vitus, Exciter, Slaughter, Sadistic Intent, Aura Noir, Possessed, Sarcòfago, Poison (Ger),\r\nSlaughter Lord, Necrovore, Morbid, Hellhammer/Celtic Frost/Triptykon, Running Wild, Venom, Darkthrone, Bathory,\r\nBeherit, Belial, Winter e altri.', 'Death, black, death/black, doom, death/doom, old school grindcore, old school thrash, classic hard rock/heavy/speed metal.', 'Viaggiare, Musica, Cucina, Alcool, Occultismo, Concerti'),
(25, 'Legnago (VR)', '11/04/1988', '', 'Sandman.jpg', 'Dark Tranquillity; In Flames; Iron Maiden; Nevermore; Metallica; Sentenced; Slipknot; Anthrax; Megadeth; Slayer;\r\nCorrosion of Conformity; Death; Fear Factory; Machine Head; System of a Down; Novembre; Burzum; Alcest; Klimt 1918', 'Death melodico; Death; Thrash; Classica; Alternative metal; Black; Blues', 'Musica tutta; cinema splatter, horror e b-movies; calcio; arti visive; letteratura; diritto'),
(26, 'Venezia', '16/08/1988', '', 'Bose_Einhorn.jpg', 'Arkona, Korpiklaani, Turisas, Tyr, Black Messiah, Rammstein, In Extremo, Akphaezya, Helium Vola, Cruachan,\r\nDiablo Swing Orchestra, Diabula Rasa, Melvins, MC5, Damned, Alaska y Dinarama/y los Pegamoides, Adam and the Ants,\r\nSiouxsie and the Banshees, Oliver Onions, Feuerschwanz, Coppelius, Johnny Cash', 'Epic, folk, darkwave, avantgarde, synth pop, krautrock', 'Viaggi, natura, computer grafica, arte, sport');

